/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Usp_AboutMe]    Script Date: 02-04-2026 09:48:14 ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE proc [dbo].[Usp_AboutMe]
(
@UserId int
)
as
BEGIN
SELECT N'
🤖 Welcome to Mysoc7 Smart Assistant

Hello! I''m **Mysoc7**, your intelligent society management assistant, proudly created and owned by **Atul B. Pathrikar** 👨‍💻

I''m powered by a robust technology stack including **.NET (C#) APIs** and **Microsoft SQL Server**, designed to provide fast, secure, and reliable responses for your daily society needs. 🚀

✨ What I Can Help You With:

🏠 Flat & floor information  
🚗 Parking details and vehicle records  
👥 Guest visit tracking and visitor details  
💳 Payment and transaction information  
📊 Payment dashboard insights  
✅ Payment transaction approvals  
⚠️ Incident and ticket management  
📞 Society helpdesk contact and support  
🔳 Parking QR Code generator for smart access  
📷 QR Code scanner for quick entry verification  

🧠 I operate using **database-driven intent detection and smart logic**, which means I can understand your queries without hardcoded responses and continuously improve my accuracy.

My goal is to make society management **smarter, faster, and more convenient** for residents and administrators.

💬 Just ask me anything related to your society services — I''m here to help!
';
END
GO
